precis:
Order directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue amending the Proclamation
Establishing the OSHAWA HARBOUR COMMISSION in order to update some of the
French terminology used therein so that it corresponds to the terminology
used in the Revised Statutes of Canada, 1985.
